manifests.contents:
[[bin]]
path = "server/main.rs"
name = "datacapsule_server"
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
edition = "2024"
required-features = []

[package]
name = "datacapsule"
edition = "2024"
version = "0.0.1"

[workspace]
members = ["capsulelib", "server", "client", "examples/basic", "examples/test"]

[dependencies]
anyhow = "1.0.100"
fjall = "2.11.2"
sha2 = "0.10.9"

[dependencies.crypto]
version = "0.5.1"
features = ["signature"]

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1.48.0"
features = ["full"]

[package]
name = "datacapsule-capsulelib"
edition = "2024"
version = "0.0.1"

[dependencies]
aes = "0.8.4"
anyhow = "1.0.100"
ctr = "0.9.2"
ed25519 = "2.2.3"
fjall = "2.11.2"
log = "0.4.29"
memoize = "0.5.1"
pretty_env_logger = "0.5.0"
serde_json = "1.0.145"
sha2 = "0.10.9"

[dependencies.crypto]
version = "0.5.1"
features = ["signature"]

[dependencies.ed25519-dalek]
version = "2.2.0"
features = ["serde"]

[dependencies.generic-array]
version = "1.3.5"
features = ["alloc"]

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0.228"
features = ["derive"]

[lib]
path = "lib.rs"
name = "datacapsule_capsulelib"
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
edition = "2024"
required-features = []
crate-type = ["lib"]

[package]
name = "datacapsule-userlib"
edition = "2024"
version = "0.0.1"

[dependencies]
anyhow = "1.0.100"

[lib]
path = "lib.rs"
name = "datacapsule_userlib"
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
edition = "2024"
required-features = []
crate-type = ["lib"]

[[bin]]
path = "src/main.rs"
name = "datacapsule-basic"
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
edition = "2024"
required-features = []

[package]
name = "datacapsule-basic"
edition = "2024"
version = "0.0.1"

[dependencies]
anyhow = "1.0.100"
hex-literal = "1.1.0"
log = "0.4.29"
pretty_env_logger = "0.5.0"
rand = "0.9.2"

[dependencies.capsulelib]
path = "../../capsulelib"
package = "datacapsule-capsulelib"

[dependencies.ed25519-dalek]
version = "2.2.0"
features = ["rand_core"]

[dependencies.rand_core]
version = "0.9.3"
features = ["os_rng", "std"]

[[bin]]
path = "src/main.rs"
name = "datacapsule-testing"
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
edition = "2024"
required-features = []

[package]
name = "datacapsule-testing"
edition = "2024"
version = "0.0.1"

[dependencies]
anyhow = "1.0.100"
hex-literal = "1.1.0"
log = "0.4.29"
pretty_env_logger = "0.5.0"
rand = "0.9.2"

[dependencies.capsulelib]
path = "../../capsulelib"
package = "datacapsule-capsulelib"

[dependencies.ed25519-dalek]
version = "2.2.0"
features = ["rand_core"]

[dependencies.rand_core]
version = "0.9.3"
features = ["os_rng", "std"]

[[bin]]
path = "main.rs"
name = "datacapsule_server"
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
edition = "2024"
required-features = []

[package]
name = "datacapsule-server"
edition = "2024"
version = "0.0.1"

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1.48.0"
features = ["full"]
